<br>
The &quot;right group&quot; always includes 2 level 61+ mages. In our case, it usually includes 2 level 65 mages, both with Sun Vortex. Add on a 61+ warrior and cleric, and you can put just about any other 2 classes.<br>
<br>
We'll generally use a 65 war with 135AAs and we can then substitute a shaman or druid for the cleric and fill the group with just about any variable and we're fine. <br>
<br>
The cleric route is still handy at times, though if someone happens to get some bad aggro from the executioner and dies prematurely so they can still get their rune by getting rezzed back.<br>
